Before implementing frontend code:

1. Read AGENTS.md.
2. Read docs/architecture.md.
3. Read docs/frontend-conventions.md.
4. Read docs/coding-style.md.

Inspect an existing page or component.

Follow the same folder structure.

Keep components reusable.

Prefer hooks for business logic.

Run lint if possible.